    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "众人",
        "副净",
        "卢俊义",
        "史文恭",
        "家将",
        "燕青"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、二女将、阮小二、阮小五、三将、林冲、燕青、武松、卢俊义同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众位哥嫂请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我等奉了大哥将令，来到此处，待俺随同林贤弟与燕小哥，前去拜庄。众家哥"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嫂，在庄外埋伏不得有误。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众人",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二女将、阮小二、阮小五、三将、武松同下，龙套、上手同转场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有人么，走出一个来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家将上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家将",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "什么人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卢俊义前来拜庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家将",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "家将",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请庄主。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四下手、四英雄、史文恭同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "副净",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卢俊义前来拜庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "副净",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，师兄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义、林冲",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贤弟）（师兄）。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请坐。未知师兄贤弟驾到，某家未曾远迎，面前恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。愚兄来得卤莽，贤弟海涵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。吓，师兄为何这样打扮？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟有所不知，只因梁山及时雨宋公明，招贤纳士，结交天下英雄，除暴安良，"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "替天行道，特命愚兄前来，邀请贤弟，同上梁山，安享富贵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄此言差矣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想你我弟兄三人，同拜周侗为师，同窗学艺，练就全身武艺，谁不闻名丧胆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "林贤弟因被奸臣所害，无处可归，投奔梁山躲避，事出无奈。想师兄久居大名，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家财万贯，坐享安乐，为何也投那梁山贼寇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只因你将晁天王射死，忠义堂好汉，纷纷议论。你若执意不肯归顺，梁山众弟"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兄，就要报那一箭之仇！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "师兄吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（急三枪） 一箭仇，却因为相争斗。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贤弟，事要三思，免生后悔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想俺史文恭！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（急三枪） 俺全凭枪法优，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪怕你人马稠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好言相劝，执意不听，少时被擒，悔之晚矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听你之言，敢么是要与小弟较量么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是要与你这匹夫比试。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪个是匹夫？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是匹夫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是匹夫。来打！"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭、卢俊义、林冲同起打，打群场，众人同下。史文恭、卢俊义比枪，打快枪，夺枪双扯下。燕青上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "对八庄丁，败下，众人同追下。燕青出庄，家将上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "家将",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众庄丁，好生把守庄门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（家将下，四上手、二女将、三将、武松同上，燕青上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众家弟兄一同前往！"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、二女将、三将、燕青同下，武松耍刀下。众人同上，会阵打连环，同下。史文恭、卢俊义夺枪同"
        },
        {
          "character": "燕青",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扯上，起打，卢俊义看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你敢么是怯战么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看天色已晚，你我明日再战。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来者？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "君子。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "卢俊义",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（卢俊义、众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众庄丁，后面歇息。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，我与那卢俊义，数载不见，他的枪法越发精壮了，待等明日前来，只怕"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此庄有些难保。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭拉势子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看他枪法，甚是高强，"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盘旋围绕似秋霜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎当俺横冲直撞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "风入松",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫你一命亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "史文恭",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看他等初到此处，未必准备，不免三更时分，偷营劫寨便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（史文恭拉势，下。）"
        }
      ],
